text: Eugen Knoblauch (born October 19, 1910, date of death unknown) is a Swiss canoeist who competed in the 1936 Summer Olympics. In 1936 he and his partner Emil Bottlang finished sixth in the folding K-2 10000 m event. ==References== *Eugen Knoblauch's profile at Sports Reference.com Category:1910 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Canoeists at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic canoeists of Switzerland Category:Swiss male canoeists
